.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><font face="宋体">本附件系实盘点买人与实盘出借人签署《实盘点买人与实盘出借人合作协议》的重要组成部分，具有同等法律效力。</font></span></b><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"> </span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;mso-outline-level:3;background:rgb(255,255,255);"><b><span style="font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><font face="宋体">六</font></span></b><b><span style="font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><font face="宋体">、实盘点买人与实盘出借人合作分润与穿仓免责</font></span></b><b><span style="font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"> </span></b></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;background:rgb(255,255,255);"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">1、在本平台的撮合下，实盘点买人与实盘出借人协商一致，就双方秉承共享收益共担风险之原则，委托本平台进行结算实盘点买人操作盈利部分分润。</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"> </span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;background:rgb(255,255,255);"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">1）实盘点买人如若点卖结算后盈利，计算盈利部分实盘点买人与实盘出借人占比为9:1。（即实盘点买人盈利部分获得90%，实盘出借人盈利部分获得10%）</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"> </span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;background:rgb(255,255,255);"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">2）股票交易严格遵循交易所撮合机制（每手订单须有对应的对手价才能成交），加上某些时间段极端行情等因素，股票交易会有穿仓现象，即用户实际结算价格超过止盈止损、履约保证金部分。当出现穿仓情况，实盘点买人只承担履约保证金部分损失，超出履约保证金部分由实盘出借人承担。</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"> </span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;mso-outline-level:3;background:rgb(255,255,255);"><b><span style="font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><font face="宋体">五、关于以上资费标准的声明</font></span></b><b><span style="font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"> </span></b></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;background:rgb(255,255,255);"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">1、本平台声明，以上所有涉及资费标准的数据，均为平台根据市场行情阶段性调整的实时标准，该数据具有一定浮动性。</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"> </span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;background:rgb(255,255,255);"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">2、本平台关于以上资费标准不做不予调整的承诺，平台将根据客观的市场行情对资费标准进行适时调整，关于调整结果将以包括但不限于短信、邮件、平台公告等形式告知用户，并将一如既往地尊重用户在新的资费条件下是否选择继续与平台合作的权利。</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"> </span></p></div>
